    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Is your child obsessed with Star Wars and the Mandalorian? This UFO ball hovering helicopter toy is a perfect gift idea this holiday season! The mini helicopter features one of everyone’s favorite characters from the hit Disney show - Boba Fett! Made with solid and durable materials, this helicopter toy is also super-lightweight, so no worrying about it breaking anything after a rough landing. It features a coaxial rotor system to provide hovering stability and precise movements (with 2 spare rotors included). This Star Wars UFO copter uses infrared motion-sensing technology to detect nearby objects and will automatically dodge them, preventing in-flight damage. It also comes with a convenient USB charger so you can charge it just about anywhere</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Star Wars UFO Ball Helicopter Mandalorian Yoda Stormtrooper Kids Toy Mini Copter</h2>\n  <p>Is your child obsessed with Star Wars and the Mandalorian? This UFO ball hovering helicopter toy is a perfect gift idea this holiday season! The mini helicopter features one of everyone’s favorite characters from the hit Disney show - Boba Fett!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>STAR WARS HELICOPTER - Officially licensed Star Wars UFO Ball Mini Copter is an excellent flying toy for kids; featuring Boba Fett from the hit Disney franchise show the Mandalorian</li>\n    <li>DURABLE AND LIGHTWEIGHT - Made with solid and light materials that won’t break anything on a rough landing; featuring a coaxial rotor system for hovering stability and precise movements</li>\n    <li>INFRARED MOTION TECH - UFO copter uses infrared motion sensing technology to detect nearby objects and will automatically dodge them; Comes with USB charger and 2 spare rotors</li>\n    <li>EASY TO USE - Just charge it, turn it on and hold your hand underneath to keep it hovering; when you’re done, grab it or use any IR remote control to shut it down safely</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Dimensions:</strong> 10.75” x 3” x 6.3”; Weight: .35lbs; Max speed: 5mph; Recommended age: 6+; Max run time: 10mins; Max distance: 10ft; Power source: battery (1 CR2032, included)</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/toys/35654_mini_helicopter_BOBA_stock_04.jpg\" alt=\"Is your child obsessed with Star Wars and the Mandalorian\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> HELIIRSWBALL</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 813023213575</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 10.75” x 3” x 6.3”</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Made with solid and durable materials, this helicopter toy is also super-lightweight, so no worrying about it breaking anything after a rough landing. It features a coaxial rotor system to provide hovering stability and precise movements (with 2 spare rotors included).</p>\n  <p>This Star Wars UFO copter uses infrared motion-sensing technology to detect nearby objects and will automatically dodge them, preventing in-flight damage. It also comes with a convenient USB charger so you can charge it just about anywhere.</p>\n  <p>The mini copters are super easy for kids to use too - just charge it, turn it on, and have them hold their hand underneath it to keep it hovering. Once done with playtime, just grab it out of the air carefully or use any IR remote control to shut it down safely. Your little Star Wars fanatic is sure to love this toy copter!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
